WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:06.290
but an officer should respond to anyone who has thoughts of suicide by

00:00:06.290 --> 00:00:11.730
 the way any normal person would be available. Be a friend, see if you

00:00:11.730 --> 00:00:17.170
 can help help them get help. As I've said before, if you sometimes

00:00:17.170 --> 00:00:22.610
 simply being there is enough to dissuade someone from carrying out

00:00:22.610 --> 00:00:28.050
 a suicidal act.

